<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Highland Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">For years, both homebuyers and investors have been attracted to the community in Highland Park for its wide range of housing options, convenient transportation and myriad of recreational opportunities including shopping malls, schools and churches. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Available at an average price of around $525,000, the homes for sale in Highland Park typically include single family homes, townhouses and apartment condominiums. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighboring Nose Hill Park and Highland Golf Course offer abundant recreational opportunities for the residents.</p>
        </div>
